column16: Evan Gattis grounds into a force out, shortstop J.   Hardy to second baseman Steve Pearce.   Carlos Correa out at 2nd.
Carlos Correa reaches on a throwing error by third baseman Pedro Alvarez.   Alex Bregman to 3rd.
Tyler White flies out to right fielder Mark Trumbo.
Alex Bregman doubles (7) on a line drive to left fielder Hyun Soo Kim.   George Springer scores.
George Springer doubles (24) on a line drive to center fielder Nolan Reimold.
Tony Kemp grounds out, pitcher Ryan Flaherty to second baseman Steve Pearce to first baseman Caleb Joseph.
Jason Castro homers (9) on a fly ball to right field.
